You should give up.

36
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,640
Yi, hurry and get up.

37
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,670
I chose the song.

38
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,960
It has nothing to do with her.

39
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:21,430
You...

40
00:02:22,990 --> 00:02:24,550
How dare you defend her?

41
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,590
Mother, you wouldn't need

42
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:26,640
to fear other people's criticisms

43
