All this while,

45
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,800
Yi has been working tirelessly

46
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,270
to manage the Water Festival.

47
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,829
It's fine that you're not helping her.

48
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,150
