I'm begging you two!

63
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,110
It's my fault!

64
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:57,360
I'm to blame.

65
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,800
I shouldn't have gifted
that lip balm to anyone!

66
00:02:58,920 --> 00:02:59,200
It's my fault!

67
00:02:59,200 --> 00:02:59,710
Stop fighting!

68
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:00,430
It's all your fault.

69
00:03:06,550 --> 00:03:07,830
Today's a huge occasion.

70
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:08,830
You two

71
