It's all because of her!

78
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:25,240
[Yanniang from Caiyun Troupe]

79
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,270
That's an allergy
triggered by Chinese yam.

80
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,710
Although she has applied medicine,

81
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:32,670
it'll take at least six hours

82
00:03:33,210 --> 00:03:34,360
for the swelling to go away.

83
00:03:35,210 --> 00:03:35,960
That won't do.

84
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,320
I need to perform

85
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,040
in less than an hour.

86
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:39,270
Physician,

87
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:40,590
are there any other solutions?

88
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,430
I'm sorry.

89
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:43,590
Farewell.

90
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,360
Why would there be Chinese yam extract

91
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,710
in a lip balm?

92
00:03:48,829 --> 00:03:49,640
You should ask her.

93
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,920
How many times have I told you?

94
00:03:50,990 --> 00:03:51,800
This has nothing to do with me.

95
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:53,079
Feiniang,

96
00:03:53,670 --> 00:03:55,150
I just bought this Banbianjiao Lip Balm.

97
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:55,829
It's for you.

98
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,520
If you put this on and perform,

99
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,320
I'm sure you can be outstanding.

100
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:02,270
I'm outstanding
because of my acting skills,

101
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,800
not because of anything else.

102
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,240
You do make it sound good.

103
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:06,550
If you're that capable,

104
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,830
