105
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:09,550
You should perform without any makeup.

106
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:13,790
Meng, I'll take it
if she doesn't want it.

107
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,270
I bought this

108
00:04:15,350 --> 00:04:16,709
for Feiniang.

109
00:04:17,149 --> 00:04:17,790
If you want one,

110
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,029
I'll buy it for you next time.

111
