116
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:31,200
with the lip balm.

117
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:32,830
I didn't even open the box.

118
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,080
How could I tamper with it

119
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:34,790
without touching it?

120
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,590
Everyone knows
that you're a lowborn child from Nanwu.

121
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,440
You have plenty of underhanded means.

122
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,440
Who are you calling a lowborn child?

123
00:04:39,470 --> 00:04:40,080
You!

124
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,030
You're a lowborn child!

125
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:42,270
Stop arguing.

126
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,560
This box itself

127
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,560
looks fine.

128
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:46,470
Mr. Meng,

129
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,390
where did you buy this lip balm?

130
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:51,710
I bought it from the rouge stall

131
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,680
to the west of the city.

132
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,470
Did you take it with you

133
00:04:54,790 --> 00:04:55,680
after buying it

134
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,440
without leaving it elsewhere?

135
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:00,080
During my performance,

136
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:01,270
I left it

137
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:01,880
on the table.

138
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,390
It's because of this wretch.

139
00:05:04,710 --> 00:05:05,710
She didn't want me to get on stage

140
00:05:05,710 --> 00:05:06,590
and perform Phoenix Hairpin.

141
00:05:07,150 --> 00:05:08,000
She was afraid I might outshine her.

142
00:05:10,150 --> 00:05:12,520
Is Phoenix Hairpin
the song Mother had chosen?

143
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:16,560
Let's forget about the lip balm.

144
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,830
The performance will begin soon.

145
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,350
Judging from Yanniang's appearance,

146
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,350
