153
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,909
Yi, I have an idea.

154
00:05:45,590 --> 00:05:49,680
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

155
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,320
The Zhu family did a great job

156
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,680
with this year's

157
00:05:59,909 --> 00:06:00,760
Water Festival.

158
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,640
The Zhu family truly excels

159
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,230
