all this while.

163
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,760
Wasn't Madam Yi

164
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:12,520
the one handling the event?

165
00:06:13,150 --> 00:06:13,910
Madam Lu,

166
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:15,590
if you didn't have
a capable daughter-in-law like Yi,

167
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:17,390
I suppose we wouldn't get to enjoy
a performance like Phoenix Hairpin.

168
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,470
Ladies, I'm sure you all are kidding.

169
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,880
I'm still young.

170
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,520
It's all thanks to
Mother's excellent arrangement.

171
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,000
I was merely her assistant.

172
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:25,640
Let's enjoy the performance.

173
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:26,830
It'll begin soon.

174
00:06:27,470 --> 00:06:30,230
Excellent!

175
00:06:30,910 --> 00:06:34,270
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

176
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:36,560
Excellent!

