00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:34,610
♪No word to her can go♪

192
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:40,080
♪No, no, no♪

193
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:45,240
- Great!
- Bravo!

194
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,870
Caiyun Troupe does live up to its name.

195
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:47,830
That was superb!

196
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,830
Madam Yi, Yan is missing!

197
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:50,320
It was great.

198
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,400
That was an excellent performance.

199
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:55,960
How could she be missing?

200
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:56,830
Wasn't she with you

201
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:57,560
all the time?

202
00:08:57,710 --> 00:08:59,040
I was buying some osmanthus cake.

203
00:08:59,110 --> 00:09:00,320
She went missing when I turned around.

204
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,080
The streets are crowded tonight.

205
00:09:02,230 --> 00:09:03,590
Nothing must happen to her.

206
00:09:04,230 --> 00:09:04,800
Madam Yi.

207
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:05,830
Commandant Xie.

208
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:07,400
What happened? Why the rush?

209
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,470
Yan is missing.

210
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:09,920
Can you help us to look for her?

211
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,680
Calm down.

212
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,560
How about this?
Let's split up and look for her.

213
00:09:12,990 --> 00:09:14,080
All right. Thank you.

214
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,750
Zhu, search that area.

215
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:16,510
I'll search there.

216
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:46,750
Mr. Yu.

217
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,710
Why are you observing
the performance from here?

218
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,750
The view here is amazing.

219
00:09:54,710 --> 00:09:56,750
The groom on the boat

220
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:59,110
resembled you.

221
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:02,870
Is that so?

222
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:08,200
Both of us have two eyes, a nose,

223
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,230
and a mask.

224
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,040
That's why we look alike.

225
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:18,590
What is this?

226
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:27,680
When I just came back,

227
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,350
Mr. Meng said he was sick.

228
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:31,230
He requested me

229
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:33,040
to perform on his behalf.

230
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:33,870
You didn't need

231
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:35,470
to expose me like that.

232
00:10:38,110 --> 00:10:38,960
Is that so?

233
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,830
I insisted on doing it.

234
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:51,400
But why?

235
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,470
It's because I don't want you

236
00:10:52,470 --> 00:10:53,350
to be married to someone else.

237
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:56,350
What? I couldn't hear you.

238
00:11:02,010 --> 00:11:02,990
It's because I don't want you

239
00:11:02,990 --> 00:11:03,960
to be married to someone else,

240
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,040
even if it's an act.

241
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,630
Madam, we're in trouble.

242
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:34,160
Feiniang had sprained her ankle.

243
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:35,750
What?

244
00:11:36,210 --> 00:11:37,470
Miss Fei, are you okay?

245
00:11:37,750 --> 00:11:38,800
What should we do?

246
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,960
The performance will begin soon.

247
00:11:40,610 --> 00:11:41,400
Here, sit down.

248
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:43,280
Our priority tonight

249
00:11:43,380 --> 00:11:44,200
is the Water Festival.

250
00:11:44,590 --> 00:11:46,040
But the ceremonial dance,
the most important part,

251
00:11:46,110 --> 00:11:47,080
is now impossible.

252
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,510
The Zhu family

253
00:11:48,710 --> 00:11:49,830
is utterly embarrassed!

254
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:53,110
You're something else!

255
00:11:53,230 --> 00:11:54,440
You knew that you had to perform,

256
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,680
yet you were still careless.

257
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:56,560
Where's Yi?

258
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,440
Where did she go?

259
00:11:59,110 --> 00:11:59,960
Madam,

260
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:00,960
we've searched

261
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,320
the entire Yunshui House.

262
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:04,080
We never saw Madam Yi.

263
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:06,110
She must be trying to avoid me.

264
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,510
She wants me

265
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,040
to clean up her mess.

266
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,350
Where did Yi go?

267
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,160
She cares about
the Water Festival the most.

268
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,750
She wouldn't leave
without any valid reasons.

269
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:15,510
What exactly happened?

270
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,280
Yan?

271
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:18,560
Madam.

272
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:19,680
Have you seen a girl around?

273
00:12:19,710 --> 00:12:20,590
Have you?

274
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:21,680
No.

275
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:22,830
Yan!

276
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,750
Have you seen a girl around?

277
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:25,470
No, I haven't.

278
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:26,160
Miss Fei,

279
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:27,800
is there anyone in the troupe

280
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,470
who can replace you?

281
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,110
The ceremonial dance is very difficult.

282
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:33,230
No one in the troupe can replace me.

283
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,400
By chance, I learned some dances

284
00:12:37,470 --> 00:12:38,470
in my childhood.

285
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:39,630
All this while, I've been serving

